reviewText: It is not as good as the 2008 award-winning Honduran film, "Angelina," but it is close. Amazon should create a "2 for 1" deal and sell them together, and they'd have a best seller.

If you've seen this box in the store, you may have noticed the running time listed as 130 minutes.  This is very deceptive.  The feature is only 48 minutes long - the rest is bonus features which my small children have very little, if any, interest in using.
